NexaSign — packages/ee/ replacement

This directory in the upstream Documenso project contained proprietary
Enterprise-Edition code licensed under the "Documenso Commercial License"
(Copyright (c) 2023 Documenso, Inc).

In NexaSign, ALL code in this directory has been REPLACED with an
independent re-implementation, written from scratch by NexaStack contributors
and licensed under the GNU Affero General Public License v3.0
(the same license that covers the rest of the NexaSign repository — see
the LICENSE file at the repository root).

The replacement provides stub / no-op implementations of the same
public exports, so that the rest of the Documenso-derived codebase (which
imports from `@documenso/ee/*`) continues to compile and run without
modification. The Enterprise-specific features (Stripe billing, SSO /
Organisation-Authentication Portal, Email-Domains, 21 CFR, Embed
white-label) are DISABLED in NexaSign. The corresponding functions either
return safe defaults ("unlimited" quotas for self-hosters) or throw an
explicit "feature not available in the NexaSign AGPL edition" error.

This replacement ships under AGPL-3.0-or-later. See FEATURES for the list
of Enterprise features that are intentionally unavailable, and the
repository root LICENSE file for the full AGPL-3.0 license text.
